{"id":389376,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/04/【图说天朝】故技重施/","date":"2015-04-16T10:55:46Z","modified":"2016-02-12T01:26:22Z","title":"【图说天朝】故技重施","content":"<p>知名网络漫画家巴丢草（<a href=\"twitter.com/badiucao\">@badiucao</a>）今日突然遭到疑似网络水军发文抹黑和推特骚扰的双重围攻，与<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/08/%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%95%E5%AE%B9%E9%9B%AA%E6%9D%91%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%80%E6%B4%BE%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%9B%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91/\">作家慕容雪村去年的遭遇</a>颇为相似。</p>\n<p>2014年8月，推特上出现了一系列共10篇题为《<a href=\"http://blog.wenxuecity.com/myblog/66831/201408/23774.html\">慕容雪村的前世今生</a>》的文章，对中国大陆知名作家慕容雪村进行密集攻击。其中除了给慕容雪村扣上诸如“毫无人性的变态伪作家”、“社会负能量传递者”、“名副其实的伪公知”等帽子外，更花大量笔墨叙述了他所谓的淫乱史，称其与多名女子偷情等。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/08/%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%95%E5%AE%B9%E9%9B%AA%E6%9D%91%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%80%E6%B4%BE%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%9B%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91/\">作家慕容雪村疑遭当局派水军抹黑</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/01/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%EF%BD%9C%E5%8D%BF%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%BF%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%96%E5%AE%A3%E3%80%8D%E4%BE%B5%E5%8D%A0%E5%A4%96%E7%B6%B2%E8%BC%BF%E8%AB%96%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93/\">泡泡｜卿子衿：五毛「外宣」侵占外網輿論空間</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/09/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AB%E6%88%91%E8%80%81%E6%9D%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E3%80%8C%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F/\">大家都叫我老杨：推特上有多少「新五毛」？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/09/%E7%BF%BB%E5%A2%99-%E8%80%81%E6%9D%A8%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E3%80%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%87%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/\">大家都叫我老杨 | 「新五毛」的推文分析</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/07/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E5%A3%B0-%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7-%E5%A0%AA%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E5%85%9A%EF%BC%9F/\">德国之声 | 推特“假账号” 堪比“五毛党”？</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/CCsp69IVIAAaCFX.png\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/CCsp69IVIAAaCFX.png\" alt=\"CCsp69IVIAAaCFX\" width=\"385\" height=\"685\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>巴丢草<a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/588610269300924417\"> <strong>@badiucao</strong></a>: 突然收到五毛在推特的集体围攻，人身攻击加色情诽谤</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/CCs6q92UIAAAMDV.png\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/CCs6q92UIAAAMDV.png\" alt=\"CCs6q92UIAAAMDV\" width=\"385\" height=\"684\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>巴丢草 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/588628686271746048\"><strong>@badiucao</strong></a>: 五毛就发这一条信息骚扰我…这样真的有用么</p></blockquote>\n<p>水军<a href=\"http://www.mingjingnews.com/MIB/Blog/blog.aspx?ID=00005948\">博主一</a>——共2篇博文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/Screen-Shot-2015-04-16-at-2.50.58-AM.png\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/Screen-Shot-2015-04-16-at-2.50.58-AM.png\" alt=\"水军2\" width=\"575\" height=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>水军<a href=\"http://blog.wenxuecity.com/myoverview/67688/\">博主二</a>——专业户：<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/Screen-Shot-2015-04-16-at-2.49.54-AM.png\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/Screen-Shot-2015-04-16-at-2.49.54-AM.png\" alt=\"水军1\" width=\"276\" height=\"226\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016,21627],"tags":[20203,8635,20773,9250,24160,8604,13826,11848,27151,15372]}